  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Unchained Rogue Skill Unlock</strong><br/><br/><p>With sufficient ranks in Stealth, you earn the following.</p><p><b>5 Ranks: </b>Reduce the Stealth penalty from sniping by 10.</p><p><b>10 Ranks: </b>Stealth check penalties for moving quickly are halved, including the ability unlocked at 5 ranks, moving full speed, and reaching concealment after creating a distraction.</p><p><b>15 Ranks: </b>If you attack after successfully using Stealth, your target is denied its Dexterity bonus against all attacks that you make before the end of your turn.</p><p><b>20 Ranks: </b>If you attack after successfully using Stealth, your target is denied its Dexterity bonus against all attacks that you make before the beginning of your next turn.</p>",
